# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:377
msgid "Remove Gaps"
msgstr "Ukloni praznine"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:378
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Remove Gap` and :guilabel:`Remove All Gaps` options help you "
"quickly eliminate gaps between clips on the timeline by rippling (i.e., "
"shifting) subsequent clips to close the gap. These options can be accessed "
"via the context menu and are only available when gaps are detected."
msgstr ""
"Opcije :guilabel:`Ukloni prazninu` i :guilabel:`Ukloni sve praznine` pomažu "
"vam brzo ukloniti praznine između isječaka na vremenskoj liniji pomicanjem "
"(tj. pomakom) sljedećih isječaka kako bi se praznina zatvorila. Ove opcije "
"su dostupne putem kontekstnog izbornika i dostupne su samo kada se otkriju "
"praznine."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:381
msgid ""
"**Remove Gap:** - This option deletes a specific gap between two clips on "
"the timeline. Right-click on the gap between clips to access the :guilabel:"
"`Remove Gap` option. - Usage: Use this option to quickly eliminate a "
"specific gap caused by trimming or using the razor tool."
msgstr ""
"**Ukloni prazninu:** - Ova opcija briše određenu prazninu između dva isječka "
"na vremenskoj liniji. Desni klik na prazninu između isječaka za pristup "
"opciji :guilabel:`Ukloni prazninu`. - Upotreba: Koristite ovu opciju za brzo "
"uklanjanje određene praznine uzrokovane rezanjem ili korištenjem alata "
"britve."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:385
msgid ""
"**Remove All Gaps:** - This option removes all gaps between clips on the "
"timeline for the entire track. Right-click on the track name to access the :"
"guilabel:`Remove All Gaps` option. - Usage: Ideal for tracks that contain "
"back-to-back clips, such as a photo slideshow, where no gaps are desired."
msgstr ""
"**Ukloni sve praznine:** - Ova opcija uklanja sve praznine između isječaka "
"na vremenskoj liniji za cijelu stazu. Desni klik na naziv staze za pristup "
"opciji :guilabel:`Ukloni sve praznine`. - Upotreba: Idealno za staze koje "
"sadrže isječke jedan do drugog, poput prezentacije fotografija, gdje nisu "
"poželjne praznine."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:391
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Remove Clip` option lets you delete a clip from the timeline. "
"Removing clips is an essential part of organizing your project and getting "
"rid of unwanted sections. Removing a clip can also impact the surrounding "
"clips. If you want to clean up the gap that remains after deleting a clip, "
"you have a few options to automatically adjust your timeline."
msgstr ""
"Opcija :guilabel:`Ukloni isječak` omogućuje vam brisanje isječka s vremenske "
"linije. Uklanjanje isječaka je ključni dio organizacije vašeg projekta i "
"uklanjanja neželjenih dijelova. Uklanjanje isječka može utjecati i na okolne "
"isječke. Ako želite očistiti prazninu koja ostane nakon brisanja isječka, "
"imate nekoliko opcija za automatsko prilagođavanje vremenske linije."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:395
msgid ""
"**How to Remove a Clip:** To delete a clip, simply select it and press :kbd:"
"`Delete` on your keyboard, or right-click the clip and choose :guilabel:"
"`Remove Clip` from the context menu. You can also select multiple clips at "
"once by holding down the :kbd:`Ctrl` key and clicking on additional clips, "
"then remove them all at once."
msgstr ""
"**Kako ukloniti isječak:** Za brisanje isječka jednostavno ga odaberite i "
"pritisnite :kbd:`Delete` na tipkovnici, ili desni klik na isječak i "
"odaberite :guilabel:`Ukloni isječak` iz kontekstnog izbornika. Također "
"možete odabrati više isječaka istovremeno držeći :kbd:`Ctrl` i klikajući na "
"dodatne isječke, zatim ih sve ukloniti odjednom."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:399
msgid ""
"**Ripple Delete:** If you want to delete a clip and automatically remove the "
"empty space (gap) it leaves behind, use the **Ripple Delete** feature by "
"pressing :kbd:`Shift+Delete`. This will shift all the remaining clips and "
"transitions on the track to the left, filling in the gap and keeping your "
"timeline smooth and continuous."
msgstr ""
"**Ripple Delete:** Ako želite izbrisati isječak i automatski ukloniti prazni "
"prostor (prazninu) koji ostavlja, koristite značajku **Ripple Delete** "
"pritiskom na :kbd:`Shift+Delete`. Ovo će pomaknuti sve preostale isječke i "
"prijelaze na stazi ulijevo, zatvarajući prazninu i održavajući vašu "
"vremensku liniju glatkom i kontinuiranom."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:404
msgid ""
"**Remove Gap:** After deleting a clip, if you have gaps left in your "
"timeline that you want to remove, simply right-click in the empty space and "
"choose :guilabel:`Remove Gap`. This action will shift all clips and "
"transitions to the left, closing the gap and maintaining the flow of your "
"video."
msgstr ""
"**Ukloni prazninu:** Nakon brisanja isječka, ako na vremenskoj liniji ostanu "
"praznine koje želite ukloniti, jednostavno desni klik na prazni prostor i "
"odaberite :guilabel:`Ukloni prazninu`. Ova radnja će pomaknuti sve isječke i "
"prijelaze ulijevo, zatvarajući prazninu i održavajući tok vašeg videa."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:410
msgid ""
"**Example**: If you have a clip that’s no longer needed, such as an intro "
"you’ve decided not to use, you can quickly select it and either delete it or "
"use **Ripple Delete** to remove it and shift everything left to close the "
"gap."
msgstr ""
"**Primjer**: Ako imate isječak koji vam više nije potreban, poput uvoda koji "
"ste odlučili ne koristiti, možete ga brzo odabrati i izbrisati ili koristiti "
"**Ripple Delete** za uklanjanje i pomicanje svega ulijevo kako biste "
"zatvorili prazninu."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:412
msgid ""
"For more advanced editing options and shortcuts, refer to the :ref:"
"`clips_cutting_slicing_ref` section."
msgstr ""
"Za naprednije opcije uređivanja i prečace, pogledajte odjeljak :ref:"
"`clips_cutting_slicing_ref`."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:415
msgid "Effects"
msgstr "Efekti"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:416
msgid ""
"In addition to the many clip properties which can be animated and adjusted, "
"you can also drop an effect directly onto a clip from the effects dock. Each "
"effect is represented by a small colored letter icon. Clicking the effect "
"icon will populate the properties of that effect, and allow you to edit (and "
