msgid "Origin X and Origin Y"
msgstr "Porijeklo X i Porijeklo Y"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:657
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Origin X` and :guilabel:`Origin Y` properties are key-frame "
"curves that define the rotation origin point's position in percentages. The "
"range for these curves is -1 to 1. See :ref:`clip_transform_ref`."
msgstr ""
"Svojstva :guilabel:`Origin X` i :guilabel:`Origin Y` su krivulje ključnih "
"okvira koje definiraju položaj točke porijekla rotacije u postocima. Raspon "
"ovih krivulja je od -1 do 1. Vidi :ref:`clip_transform_ref`."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:660
msgid ""
"**Usage Example:** Rotating a clip around a specific point, such as a "
"character's pivot joint."
msgstr ""
"**Primjer upotrebe:** Rotiranje isječka oko određene točke, poput zgloba "
"pivotne točke lika."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:661
msgid ""
"**Tip:** Set the origin point to achieve controlled and natural-looking "
"rotations during animations."
msgstr ""
"**Savjet:** Postavite točku porijekla za postizanje kontroliranih i "
"prirodnih rotacija tijekom animacija."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:666
msgid "Clip Parent"
msgstr "Roditelj isječka"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:667
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Parent` property of a clip sets the initial keyframe values "
"to the parent object. For example, if many clips all point to the same "
"parent clip, they will inherit all their default properties, such as "
"``location_x``, ``location_y``, ``scale_x``, ``scale_y``, etc... This can be "
"very useful in certain circumstances, such as when you have many clips that "
"need to move or scale together."
msgstr ""
"Svojstvo :guilabel:`Parent` isječka postavlja početne vrijednosti ključnih "
"okvira na roditeljski objekt. Na primjer, ako mnogi isječci pokazuju na isti "
"roditeljski isječak, naslijedit će sva njegova zadana svojstva, poput "
"``location_x``, ``location_y``, ``scale_x``, ``scale_y`` itd. Ovo može biti "
"vrlo korisno u određenim situacijama, kao kada imate mnogo isječaka koji "
"trebaju zajedno mijenjati položaj ili veličinu."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:671
msgid ""
"**Usage Example:** Creating complex animations by establishing a parent-"
"child relationship between clips."
msgstr ""
"**Primjer upotrebe:** Stvaranje složenih animacija uspostavljanjem odnosa "
"roditelj-dijete između isječaka."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:672
msgid ""
"**Tip:** Utilize this property to propagate changes from the parent clip to "
"child clips for consistent animations."
msgstr ""
"**Savjet:** Iskoristite ovo svojstvo za prenošenje promjena s roditeljskog "
"isječka na dječje isječke radi dosljednih animacija."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:673
msgid ""
"**Tip:** You can also set the ``parent`` attribute to a ``Tracker`` or "
"``Object Detector`` tracked object, so the clip follows the location and "
"scale of a tracked object. Also see :ref:`effect_parent_ref`."
msgstr ""
"**Savjet:** Također možete postaviti atribut ``parent`` na objekt praćen "
"Trackerom ili Detektorom objekata, tako da isječak prati položaj i veličinu "
"praćenog objekta. Vidi također :ref:`effect_parent_ref`."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:677
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Position` property determines the clip's position on the "
"timeline in seconds, with 0.0 indicating the beginning."
msgstr ""
"Svojstvo :guilabel:`Position` određuje položaj isječka na vremenskoj liniji "
"u sekundama, pri čemu 0.0 označava početak."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:679
msgid ""
"**Usage Example:** Timing a clip's appearance to coincide with specific "
"events in the project."
msgstr ""
"**Primjer upotrebe:** Sinkronizacija pojavljivanja isječka s određenim "
"događajima u projektu."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:680
msgid ""
"**Tip:** Adjust the position to synchronize clips with audio cues or visual "
