# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:732
msgid ""
"**Tip:** Use shear properties for creating slanted or skewed animations."
msgstr ""
"**Savjet:** Koristite svojstva nagiba za stvaranje nagnutih ili iskrivljenih "
